View Fulfillment While it Happens

View every fulfillment step as it flows through the fulfillment process. See the status of every step and its dependencies in the Fulfillment Plan graphical interface. With a single click from the plan, you can change the state of a fulfillment step or see its details.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

Why: In the Fulfillment Plan Viewer, Fulfillment Operators can see what's happening with their order. They can see the dependencies between steps, which steps have been completed, and so on. They can also complete a task directly from their workspace, and get more information about that task.

How: From the App Launcher, find and select Fulfillment Plans, and then edit a fulfillment plan or create one.
title: Viewing Fulfillment in Real-Time
